data.description: SAY YES 2 THE VILLAGES @ BROOKMONT!! WELCOME TO 3715 BROOK HOLLOW DR YOUR HOMES HOME! As you walk into this Oversized Oasis, you will be greeted by the ever-so-welcoming Foyer area that rubs shoulders with the formal dining room! As you transition through the Coffee Nook, the Kitchen awaits, which is the Heart and soul of the Home! As you enter the Kitchen, you are greeted with Granite and plenty of storage in your mahogany cabinetry! Visualize yourself preparing dinner as you gaze at the family in the dining room and den combo! Journey back through the foyer and cascade upstairs to the Primary Bedroom with a spa-like bath and oversized owner's closet! As you walk, the catwalk will lead you to the three other bedrooms on this level! Each bedroom has bathroom access and closet systems to prioritize organization! But wait, there is more! We saved the best for last! As a bonus, relax in the oversized media room as you enjoy the latest and most in-demand movies with your family. This Home is perfect and waiting for your YES !! ARE YOU READY TO SAY YES 2 THIS ADDRESS??
